<H3><PRE>

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C. How much longer will you forget me,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">        E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   O my Lord
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">            E7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   how much longer
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                                Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   will you hide your face from me?

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">          E7       Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A. I will sing to Yahweh,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">          E7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   I will sing
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                    Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   to Him who is my Saviour.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">           Am                          E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C. Look at me, answer me, Yahweh O my love;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                    E7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   give light to my eyes
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                         Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   lest I fall asleep in death.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">          E7       Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A. I will sing to Yahweh,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">          E7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   I will sing
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                    Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   to Him who is my Saviour.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C. Lest my foes say:
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                           E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   “we have prevailed over him,”
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">           E7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   lest my oppressors
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                           Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   rejoice because I have stumbled.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">          E7       Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A. I will sing to Yahweh,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">          E7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   I will sing
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                    Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   to Him who is my Saviour.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   Am                      E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C. But I, I rely upon your mercy
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">          E7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   and my heart
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                       Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   shall rejoice in your salvation.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">          E7       Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A. I will sing to Yahweh,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">          E7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   I will sing
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                    Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   to Him who is my Saviour.

